videos.description: Louisville gets out in transition as Jordan Nwora Eurosteps around a Hokie defender for an easy lay-in.
videos.headline: Nwora's sweet Eurostep leads to easy lay-in

videos.description: The Hokies are making a run as Kerry Blackshear Jr. is left wide-open for a nice two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Blackshear throws down monster slam

videos.description: Virginia Tech turns defense to offense as they come up with a steal and Ahmed Hill rises for a nasty two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Hill skies for emphatic 2-handed flush

videos.description: Louisville head coach Chris Mack was not pleased with their first half and shrugs off after giving a short answer.
videos.headline: Mack not pleased with Louisville's first half
